        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'> You're all insane. Tallon, Vallon and Rallos are blue. Yes, blue. Sullon Zek is the most insanity you'll ever see in EQ, and seeing as there is ONE rule (no cursing), you'll see some true PvP. No more of this X-teaming madness that plagues the other servers. As for Sullon, the fact that I can walk up to a level 1 and simply melee them in 1 round is hilarious. Especially when they're running across the world to bind. :)</P><P>Example:<BR>Level 15 in a tough spot, kills his mob, low HP. You kill him. He whines, cries, and comes back. You kill him again. And again. Once you find out how long it takes him to run back, you can get a good idea where he is bound. Have a friend watch the corpse while you wait on the other side of the zone he has to zone in. Slay him again. Repeat. Repeat this until he quits the server due to frustration, and then theres one less person to cause lag.</P><P> </font></td>
